data.description: 1-story all Brick home in Pebble Creek neighborhood of Killearn Estates. VA assumable loan at 4.375%. This Open floorplan has huge vaulted ceilings in main living area and is within walking distance to Killearn Golf & Country Club. Amenities include: Fireplace, 2-car garage, large deck, hardwood floors, and A/C in 2014. Family Room/den has closet, it was used as a 2nd TV area. Ready for immediate occupancy!
